'''Apache Wave'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://googlewavedev.blogspot.com/2010/12/introducing-apache-wave.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-09-10 |archive-date=2011-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110906081522/http://googlewavedev.blogspot.com/2010/12/introducing-apache-wave.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，按照[[Google|Google]]在2009年5月27日[[Google_I/O|Google I/O]]上的说法，是一种「个人通信和协作工具」。它是一个[[Web服务|Web服务]]、计算平台和[[通信协议|通信协议]]，旨在合并[[电子邮件|电子邮件]]、[[即时通讯|即时通讯]]、[[wiki|wiki]]和[[社交网络|社交网络]]。由悉尼分公司开发，最初进行小范围内公测<ref>{{cite news | language =en | author = | coauthors = | url =http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/pda/2009/sep/30/google-wave-beta-testing | title =Google Wave beta testing begins | work = | publisher =guardian.co.uk | pages = | date =2009-09-30 | accessdate =2009-10-16 | archive-date =2009-10-03 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20091003133033/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/pda/2009/sep/30/google-wave-beta-testing | dead-url =no }}</ref>。它有一个强大的实时协作和强大的拼写检查功能，可以自动翻译40种语言，以及许多其他的扩展。在2009年9月30日，测试Google Wave的用户数已扩大到约10万。

从2010年5月19日起，Google Wave正式向公众开放注册<ref>{{cite news | language =en | author =Stephen Shankland | coauthors = | url =http://news.cnet.com/8301-30685_3-20005394-264.html | title =Google Wave: Now open to the public begins | work = | publisher = | pages = | date =2010-05-19 | accessdate =2010-05-24 | archive-date =2013-09-14 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20130914120657/http://news.cnet.com/8301-30685_3-20005394-264.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

2010年8月4日，Google宣布停止对Google Wave的开发，对平台的维护至少延续到年底<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://googleblog.blogspot.com/2010/08/update-on-google-wave.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-08-05 |archive-date=2018-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615053510/https://googleblog.blogspot.com/2010/08/update-on-google-wave.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并在2012年1月后将Google Wave设为只读，然后在2012年4月宣布删除数据<ref>{{cite web |url=http://googleblog.blogspot.com/2011/11/more-spring-cleaning-out-of-season.html |title=Official Blog: More spring cleaning out of season |publisher=Googleblog.blogspot.com |date=2011-11-22 |accessdate=2013-06-15 |archive-date=2018-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180801034401/https://googleblog.blogspot.com/2011/11/more-spring-cleaning-out-of-season.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在此之后，Google把Google Wave交給[[Apache軟件基金會|Apache軟件基金會]]繼續發展<ref>Meyer, David. (2010-09-03) [http://www.zdnet.co.uk/news/application-development/2010/09/03/google-puts-open-source-wave-in-a-box-40089999/ Google puts open-source Wave in a 'box' | Application Development | ZDNet UK] {{Wayback|url=http://www.zdnet.co.uk/news/application-development/2010/09/03/google-puts-open-source-wave-in-a-box-40089999/ |date=20101108141436 }}. Zdnet.co.uk. Retrieved on 2010-12-14.</ref><ref>[http://www.idg.se/2.1085/1.355483/google-wave-inte-ute-ur-leken Google Wave inte ute ur leken] {{Wayback|url=http://www.idg.se/2.1085/1.355483/google-wave-inte-ute-ur-leken |date=20131203024529 }}. IDG.se. Retrieved on 2010-12-14.</ref><ref>Murphy, David. (1970-01-01) [http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2368730,00.asp Google Spins Wave Into 'Wave in a Box' for Third-Party Use | News & Opinion] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2368730,00.asp |date=20120403002038 }}. PCMag.com. Retrieved on 2010-12-14.</ref>。

此项目已在2018年1月5日关停<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://incubator.apache.org/projects/wave.html|title=Wave Incubation Status - Apache Incubator|website=incubator.apache.org|access-date=2018-04-12|archive-date=2018-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180413030428/http://incubator.apache.org/projects/wave.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 词源 ==
名称灵感来自[[Firefly|Firefly]]电视连续剧，其中被称为Wave的电子通信技术（通常是一个视频电话或视频信息）。

== API ==
Google设计了[[API|API]]，让开发者通过下面的方式使用和设计Google Wave：

* '''扩展 '''：[[bot|机器人]]程序自动执行常见任务和/或设计小工具，以扩展或改变用户交互<ref name="codepage">{{cite web|url=http://code.google.com/apis/wave/|title=Google Wave API - Google Code|publisher=Google|accessdate=2009-07-27|archive-date=2009-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090801101547/http://code.google.com/apis/wave/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* '''嵌入 '''：可以将外部站点或[[blog|blog]]的内容直接拖入到wave会话.<ref name="codepage" />。

目前已经有150多个Google Wave扩展<ref>{{cite web |url=http://wave-samples-gallery.appspot.com/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-04-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100415004922/http://wave-samples-gallery.appspot.com/ |archivedate=2010-04-15 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wextensions.com/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190127062101/http://www.wextensions.com/ |archive-date=2019-01-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

Google Wave 的扩展主要有两种类型：
* '''小工具'''
* '''机器人''' ：机器人是wave的一个自动参与者。他们可以和用户交流并和wave互动。他们可以从外部源获取信息（例如Twitter，股票报价等等），机器人API的最新版本是2.0<ref name="robotsapiv2">{{cite web|url=http://googlewavedev.blogspot.com/2010/03/introducing-robots-api-v2-rise-of.html|title=Introducing Robots API v2: The Rise of Active Robots|publisher=Google|accessdate=2010-07-26|archive-date=2017-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171105060117/http://googlewavedev.blogspot.com/2010/03/introducing-robots-api-v2-rise-of.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

